p%3EManika's%20ploy%20to%20attack%20Prithika's%20backhand%20proved%20very%20effective%20but%20that%20was%20not%20the%20strategy%20she%20had%20devised%20before%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20planned%20to%20play%20to%20her%20forehand%20as%20discussed%20with%20my%20coach%20but%20I%20was%20getting%20the%20points%20on%20her%20backhand%2C%20so%20I%20did%20not%20change%20the%20tactics.%20I%20did%20play%20a%20few%20shot%20on%20her%20forehand%20too%2C%20I%20did%20not%20want%20her%20to%20think%20that%20I%20am%20playing%20only%20on%20her%20backhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20tough%20match.%20Staying%20relaxed%20helps%20me%20both%20on%20and%20off%20the%20court.%20I%20do%20breathing%20exercises%20that%20help%20me%20during%20the%20match.I%20will%20give%20my%20best%20whoever%20I%20play%20against%20in%20the%20next%20round%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrithika's%20parents%20are%20originally%20from%20Puducherry%20but%20the%20family%20shifted%20to%20France%20in%202003.%20She%20was%20born%20in%20a%20Paris%20suburb%20a%20year%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2019-year-old%20Prithika%20had%20competed%20in%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics%2C%20making%20a%20first-round%20exit%20but%20has%20improved%20considerably%20since%20then%20as%20she%20is%20currently%20ranked%2018th%20in%20the%20world%20as%20against%2028th%20rank%20of%20Manika.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeft-handed%20Prithika%20came%20into%20the%20Olympics%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20splendid%20run%20where%20she%20made%20the%20WTT%20final%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20her%20career%20in%20June%20but%20could%20not%20find%20a%20way%20to%20go%20past%20Manika%2C%20who%20dished%20out%20a%20commanding%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20game%20was%20a%20tight%20affair%20with%20both%20players%20going%20neck%20and%20neck.%20At%208-8%2C%20Manika%20induced%20a%20backhand%20error%20from%20her%20young%20rival%20and%20closed%20the%20game%20with%20a%20ferocious%20forehand%20drive%20that%20Prithika%20could%20not%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManika%20carried%20the%20momentum%20in%20the%20second%20game%2C%20taking%20a%203-1%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrithika%20fought%20back%20to%20level%20the%20scores%2C%20inducing%20errors%20from%20the%20Indian.%20However%2C%20Manika's%20attack%20on%20Prithika's%20backhand%20got%20her%20points%20consistently.%20In%20no%20time%2C%20she%20was%20leading%209-6.%20Consecutive%20backhand%20errors%20from%20Prithika%20handed%20Manika%20the%20second%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20stopping%20the%20seasoned%20Indian%2C%20who%20got%20a%20healthy%203-0%20cushion%20in%20game%20three%20as%20Prithika%20struggled%20with%20her%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20desperate%20Prithika%20went%20all%20out%20and%20got%20her%20first%20point%20with%20a%20thumping%20forehand%20winner.%20With%20a%205-1%20lead%20in%20hand%2C%20Manika%20kept%20attacking%20the%20backhand%20side%20of%20the%20French%20player%2C%20making%20it%208-4.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrailing%205-10%2C%20Prithika%20made%20it%20a%20contest%20by%20taking%20four%20points%20in%20a%20row%20but%20Manika%20needed%20just%20one%20more%20to%20close%20the%20game.%20The%20home%20favourite%20netted%20a%20backhand%20drive%20to%20concede%20the%20game%20and%20a%203-0%20lead%20to%20the%20Indian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20ferocious%20forehand%20gave%20Manika%20a%2010-5%20lead%20in%20the%20fourth%20game%20and%20five%20match%20points.%20She%20converted%20the%20third%20when%20Prithika%20netted%20her%20backhand%20to%20win%20the%20match%20in%2037%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722309900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Flfrt8vqg_manika-batra-afp_625x300_30_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fmanika-batra-makes-table-tennis-history-becomes-first-indian-to-reach-olympics-round-of-16-6218409%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2029-year-old%20Manika%20dominated%20from%20start%20to%20finish%20for%20an%2011-9%2011-