an-for-sc-term-limits-ethics-code%2Farticleshow%2F112122850.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjoe-biden-unveils-plan-for-sc-term-limits-ethics-code%2Famp_articleshow%2F112122850.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjoe-biden-unveils-plan-for-sc-term-limits-ethics-code%2Famp_articleshow%2F112122850.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shooter%20Manu%20Bhaker%20On%20Cusp%20Of%20Historic%20First%20In%20Independent%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20ace%20shooter%20Manu%20Bhaker%20created%20history%20in%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20female%20from%20the%20sport%20in%20the%20country%20to%20win%20a%20medal.%20She%20did%20so%20in%20the%20women's%20individual%2010m%20air%20pistol%20final%2C%20clinching%20a%20bronze%20medal.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20Manu%20could%20create%20bigger%20history%20if%20she%20and%20her%20partner%20Sarabjot%20Singh%20could%20earn%20India%20another%20bronze%20medal%20in%20the%20mixed%20team%2010m%20air%20pistol%20final.%20If%20Manu%20does%20go%20on%20to%20bag%20another%20bronze%20medal%2C%20she%20would%20become%20the%20first%20athlete%20from%20Independent%20India%20to%20win%20two%20medals%20in%20the%20same%20Olympic%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20Indian%20athlete%20who%20has%20done%20so%20before%20is%20Norman%20Pritchard%20won%20two%20silver%20medals%20in%20athletics%20during%20the%201900%20Games%20when%20India%20was%20under%20British%20rule.%20After%20Pritchard%2C%20no%20Indian%20athlete%20has%20managed%20to%20win%20two%20medals%20in%20a%20single%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWinning%20this%20medal%20is%20a%20dream%20come%20true%2C%20not%20just%20for%20me%20but%20for%20everyone%20who%20has%20supported%20me.%20I%20am%20deeply%20grateful%20to%20the%20NRAI%2C%20SAI%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Youth%20Affairs%20%26amp%3B%20Sports%2C%20Coach%20Jaspal%20Rana%20sir%2C%20Haryana%20government%20and%20OGQ.%20I%20dedicate%20this%20victory%20to%20my%20country%20for%20their%20incredible%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FhnzGjNwUhv%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FhnzGjNwUhv%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Manu%20Bhaker%20(%40realmanubhaker)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frealmanubhaker%2Fstatus%2F1817558572550504903%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2028%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20Indian%20athletes%20who%20have%20won%20two%20medals%20in%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20cumulatively%20in%20their%20career.%20They%20are%20Sushil%20Kumar%20(wrestling)%20and%20PV%20Sindhu%20(badminton).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESushil%20bagged%20a%20bronze%20medal%20at%20the%20Beijing%202008%20games%20before%20earning%20a%20silver%20medal%20at%20London%202012.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20he%20became%20the%20first-ever%20individual%20athlete%20from%20India%20to%20win%20multiple%20Olympic%20medals%20post-independence%2C%20over%20two%20different%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShuttler%20Sindhu%20won%20silver%20in%20the%20Rio%20Olympics%2C%20after%20being%20beaten%20by%20Spain's%20Carolina%20Marin%20in%20the%20final.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20India%20had%20won%20a%20silver%20medal%20in%20Olympic%20badminton.%20Sindh%20later%20won%20bronze%20at%20Tokyo%202020.%20Sindhu%20is%20the%20only%20woman%20athlete%20from%20India%20to%20win%20multiple%20medals%20at%20the%20Olympic%20Games%2C%20though%20over%20two%20different%20editions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhaker's%20case%20is%20quite%20different%20from%20Shushil%20and%20Sindhu's%20as%20she%20could%20become%20the%20first%20Indian%20post-independence%20to%20bag%20two%20medals%20from%20the%20same%20Olympic%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManu%20Bhaker%20and%20Sarabjot%20Singh%20will%C2%A0be%20up%20against%20the%20Korean%20pair%20of%20Oh%20Ye%20Jin%20and%20Lee%20Wonho%20in%20the%20bronze-medal%20match.%20Manu%20and%20Sarabjot%20shot%20a%20combined%20total%20of%20580%20in%20the%20qualifier%20to%20finish%20third%20while%20the%20Korean%20duo%20sealed%204th%20spot%20with%20a%20score%20of%20579.%20On%20Day%204%20of%20the%20Olympic%20Games%2C%20the%20Indian%20duo%20would%20hope%20to%20repeat%20their%20qualification%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722307380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F7o9v1at8_manu-bhaker-afp_625x300_30_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fmanu-bhaker-on-cusp-of-historic-first-in-independent-india-could-recreate-124-year-old-feat-6219577%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20ace%20shooter%20Manu%20Bhaker%20could%20go%20on%20to%20create%20history%20on%20Day%204%20of%20the%20Paris%20Olympic%20Games%2C%20hoping%20to%20become%20the%20first%20Indian%20athlete%20from%20the%20country%20post-independence%20to%20win%20two%20medals%20in%20a%20single%20campaign.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Trump%20gunman%20was%20seen%2090%20mins%20before%20shooting'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722307362000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112122820%2Cimgsize-1005968.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-gunman-was-seen-90-mins-before-shooting%2Farticleshow%2F112122792.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112122792.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThomas%20Crooks%2C%20who%20attempted%20to%20kill%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20July%2013%2C%20was%20identified%20by%20police%20over%20an%20hour%20before%20the%20shooting.%20FBI's%20Kevin%20Rojek%20stated%2