d%20a%20lot%20more%20reminders%20when%20they're%20doing%20it%20at%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210e58f96-8edd-4df5-a436-48e59d08b7b7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20them%20make%20their%20own%20mistakes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20said%20teens%20benefit%20when%20they're%20allowed%20to%20figure%20things%20out%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20best%20way%20for%20them%20to%20grow%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20parents%2C%20if%20we%20want%20to%20raise%20dependable%20and%20successful%20teenagers%2C%20we%20have%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20let%20them%20struggle%20and%20fail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20cited%20the%20case%20of%20a%20lifeguard%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-iphone-stolen-device-protection-how-to-turn-on-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonce%20lost%20his%20iPhone%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20didn't%20contact%20her%20by%20other%20means%20to%20confirm%20his%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20texted%20a%20schedule%20to%20everybody%20every%20week%2C%20but%20he%20didn't%20get%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20pretty%20big%20mess%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20accepted%20the%20consequences.%20He%20apologized%20and%20said%20it%20would%20never%20happen%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20told%20him%2C%20'Everybody%20makes%20mistakes%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20fire%20people%20if%20you%20make%20a%20mistake%2C'%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20added.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20schedule%20you%20for%20extra%20hours%20next%20week%20because%20I%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20I%20can%20rely%20on%20you%20and%20that%20you're%20going%20to%20show%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20that%20he%20learned%20from%20that%20experience%20and%20is%20now%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%20communicators%26quot%3B%20on%20her%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20