%20halwa%20is%20being%20distributed%2C%20but%2073%25%20of%20the%20country's%20people%20are%20not%20included%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20placed%20her%20hands%20over%20her%20face.%20A%20disapproving%20nod%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reaction%20was%20not%20lost%20on%20the%20Congress%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Finance%20Minister%20is%20laughing.%20It%20is%20quite%20astonishing.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20laughing%20matter%2C%20madam.%20This%20is%20about%20caste%20census.%20It%20will%20change%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20claimed%20the%20sole%20aim%20of%20the%20Budget%20is%20to%20strengthen%20the%20framework%20of%20big%20businesses%2C%20political%20monopoly%20that%20destroys%20the%20democratic%20structure%2C%20and%20the%20deep%20state%20or%20the%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPushing%20back%2C%20BJP%20national%20general%20secretary%20(organisation)%20B%20L%20Santhosh%20posted%20on%20X%20pictures%20of%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Foundation's%20board%20members%20which%20included%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20former%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20P%20Chidambaram%2C%20and%20asked%20which%20of%20them%20belong%20to%20OBC%2C%20SC%20and%20ST%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRajiv%20Gandhi%20Foundation%20Board%20for%20your%20perusal.%20Identify%20OBCs%2C%20SCs%20and%20STs%20for%20the%20use%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20troll%20army%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20X%20along%20with%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20foundation's%20website%20showing%20its%20board%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20IT%20department%20head%20Amit%20Malviya%20alleged%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Banti-SC%2FST%20and%20OBC%26quot%3B%20since%20Independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20Congress%20which%20kept%20(the)%20Kelkar%20Committee%20recommendation%20(for%20Backward%20Commission)%20made%20in%201957%20in%20cold%20storage%20until%20PM%20Modi%20gave%20constitutional%20status%20to%20the%20OBC%20Commission%20in%202018%2C%20that%20too%20despite%20Congress'%20opposition%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Malviya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20drew%20parallels%20from%20the%20Mahabharata%2C%20and%20attacked%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20over%20the%20Budget%20saying%20that%20there's%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20fear%20in%20the%20country%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20country%20is%20now%20trapped%20in%20a%20%26quot%3BChakravyuh%20of%20lotus%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20the%20BJP's%20symbol.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722277620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Foq8e0d6g_rahul-gandhi-_625x300_29_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhis-speech-nirmala-sitharamans-viral-reaction-and-a-bjp-pushback-6217914%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nirmala%20Sitharaman's%20facepalm%20moment%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20all%20over%20the%20internet.%20It%20happened%20when%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20mentioned%20the%20traditional%20pre-Budget%20'Halwa'%20ceremony%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20diversity%20in%20the%20exercise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhis-speech-nirmala-sitharamans-viral-reaction-and-a-bjp-pushback-6217914%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhis-speech-nirmala-sitharamans-viral-reaction-and-a-bjp-pushback-6217914%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhis-speech-nirmala-sitharamans-viral-reaction-and-a-bjp-pushback-6217914%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Electric%202W%20player%20Ola%20Electric%20sets%20IPO%20price%20band%20at%20Rs%2072-76%20per%20share%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722277413000%2C