panies%2Fnews%2Fahead-of-ipo-akums-drugs-garners-rs-829-cr-from-anchor-investors-124072901403_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fahead-of-ipo-akums-drugs-garners-rs-829-cr-from-anchor-investors-124072901403_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Few%20Doctors%2C%20Nurses%20In%20Relief%20Hospitals%2C%20Bhopal%20Gas%20Survivors%20Suffer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20poignant%20statue%20commemorating%20the%20Bhopal%20gas%20tragedy%20-%20a%20child%20clinging%20to%20its%20mother%20--%20stands%20near%20the%20infamous%20Union%20Carbide%20factory.%20Dutch%20artist%20Ruth%20Waterman%20sculpted%20this%20statue%20in%201985%2C%20moved%20by%20the%20tragedy%20and%20her%20parents'%20deaths%20in%20a%20Nazi%20gas%20chamber.%20Forty%20years%20on%2C%20thousands%20of%20survivors%20of%20Bhopal%20tragedy%20continue%20to%20suffer%2C%20their%20health%20deteriorating%20with%20insufficient%20medical%20care.%20Nearly%20half%20the%20allotted%20posts%20of%20doctors%2C%20nurses%2C%20and%20paramedical%20staff%20in%20gas%20relief%20hospitals%20lie%20vacant%2C%20despite%20orders%20from%20the%20state%20High%20Court%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20appoint%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%201%2C247%20posts%20in%20gas%20relief%20hospitals%20-%20only%20749%2C%20a%20little%20over%20half%2C%20are%20filled.%20On%20May%2016%2C%202024%2C%20the%20Bhopal%20Gas%20Tragedy%20Relief%20and%20Rehabilitation%20Department%20advertised%20for%2046%20specialists%20and%2069%20medical%20officers.%20On%20June%2027%2C%202024%2C%20the%20Health%20Services%20Directorate%20ordered%20the%20posting%20of%20only%2015%20medical%20officers%20including%205%20specialists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20many%20doctors%20have%20been%20informally%20told%20that%20these%20orders%20have%20been%20cancelled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20reveal%20that%20some%20doctors%20were%20informed%20by%20the%20Cabinet%20Minister%20that%20their%20selection%20order%20was%20void.%20Dr%20Pratap%20Singh%20whose%20wife%20was%20selected%2C%20asserted%20that%20many%20doctors%20applied%20for%20deputation%2C%20but%20the%20selection%20process%20stalled%20without%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20a%20High%20Court%20directive%20on%20November%2030%2C%202023%2C%20threatening%20contempt%20proceedings%20against%20top%20officials%20for%20failing%20to%20fill%20vacancies%2C%20little%20progress%20has%20been%20made.%20The%20Health%20Department's%20May%2016%20advertisement%20yielded%20only%2015%20appointed%20doctors%2C%20and%20even%20that%20list%20was%20halted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20specialist%20doctors%2C%20including%20anaesthesiologists%2C%20hinders%20surgical%20procedures%20in%20gas%20relief%20hospitals.%20Medical%20Minister%20Rajendra%20Shukla%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BGas%20relief%20hospitals%20receive%20regular%20appointments.%20We%20aim%20to%20resolve%20these%20issues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFifteen%20doctors%20have%20been%20appointed%20across%20eight%20hospitals%2C%20and%20more%20appointments%20will%20follow%20within%20ten%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20state%20minister%20Vijay%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20ground%2C%20little%20has%20changed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoor%20Jahan%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Arif%20Nagar%2C%20struggles%20with%20severe%20health%20problems.%20%26quot%3BMy%20young%20son%20died%20due%20to%20the%20gas%3B%20he%20was%20just%20two%20years%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20I%20have%20knee%20pain%2C%20diabetes%2C%20and%20blood%20pressure%20issues.%20The%20hospitals%20have%20long%20queues%2C%20no%20doctors%2C%20and%20no%20medicines%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisplaying%20medical%20reports%20from%20a%20private%20hospital%2C%20Kammo%20Begum%2C%20another%20survivor%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20suffer%20from%20headaches%20and%20walking%20difficulties.%20Waiting%20for%20hours%20in%20a%20government%20hospital%20is%20beyond%20my%20capac