%20the%20former%20MP%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20son%20has%20got%20a%20ticket%26quot%3B.%20Karan%20Bhushan%20Singh%20has%20won%20the%20constituency%20--%20which%20his%20father%20had%20represented%20since%202009%20--%20in%20the%20general%20election%20that%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20reporters%20in%20Paraspur%20today%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20will%20never%20give%20me%20a%20chance%20now.%20I%20know%20the%20party%20will%20not%20give%20me%20a%20chance.%20I%20don't%20dream%20like%20Mungerilal.%20Those%20who%20want%20to%2C%20can%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20chief%20of%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20several%20women%20wrestlers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20massive%20row%20over%20the%20allegations%20and%20a%20weeks-long%20protest%20by%20the%20country's%20top%20wrestlers%20last%20year%2C%20he%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20top%20post%20of%20the%20Federation.%20He%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20either%20and%20his%20son%20was%20fielded%20instead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20in%20the%20case%20started%20last%20week.%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20sections%20relating%20to%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20use%20of%20force%20against%20a%20woman%20and%20criminal%20intimidation%20have%20been%20slapped%20on%20the%20heavyweight%20leader.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%2C%20denying%20any%20wrongdoing.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20have%20not%20committed%20any%20mistake%2C%20why%20will%20I%20admit%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20had%20gone%20on%20a%20tour%20of%20his%20former%20parliamentary%20constituency%20in%20Gonda%20district%20of%20UP.%20He%20had%20made%20a%20stopover%20at%20Paraspur%2C%20where%20a%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%2C%20Om%20Prakash%20Singh%2C%20had%20been%20murdered%20in%20broad%20daylight.%20He%20had%20gone%20there%20to%20meet%20the%20family%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20support%20criminals%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20police%20are%20working%20on%20the%20murder%20case.%20I%20demand%20financial%20help%20from%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722271920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fvvjfpaj8_brij-bhushan-singh-facebook-650_650x400_02_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-second-chances-im-not-mungerilal-former-wrestling-body-chief-6217150%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20MP%20and%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20chief%20Brijbhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20-%20denied%20a%20ticket%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20this%20gelection%20amid%20glare%20over%20sexual%20harassment%20allegations%20against%20him%20--%20today%20said%20he%20would%20never%20get%20a%20second%20chance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-second-chances-im-not-mungerilal-former-wrestling-body-chief-6217150%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-second-chances-im-not-mungerilal-former-wrestling-body-chief-6217150%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-second-chances-im-not-mungerilal-former-wrestling-body-chief-6217150%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Husband-Wife%20Fight%20Solved%20By%20Lok%20Adalat%20Bench%20Of%20Chief%20Justice%2C%20Kapil%20Sibal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20today%20chaired%20a%20Lok%20Adalat%20and%20shared%20the%20bench%20with%20senior%20Supreme%20Court%20Advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20a%20rare%20occasion%20at%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20and%20Mr%20Sibal%20were%20part%20of%20the%20Lok%20Adalat%20along%20with%20Justice%20JB%20Pardiwala%2C%20Justice%20Manoj%20Mishra%20and%20Supreme%20Court%20Advocate%20On%20Record%20Association%20President%2C%20Vipin%20Nair.%20The%20cases%20are%20heard%20between%20July%2029%20and%20August%202%20and%20are%20heard%20from%202%20pm%20after%20the%20court's%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20a%20case%20that%20came%20to%20one%20of%20the%20Lok%20Adalats%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20today%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20remember%20a%20case%20in%20which%20the%20husband%20had%20filed%20divorce%20proceedings%20in%20Patiala%20House%20Court%20and%20his%20wife%20had%20filed%20maintenance%20proceedings%20and%20filed%20for%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20children.%20Both%20of%20them%20came%20together%20in%20the%20pre-Lok%20Adalat%20sitting%20and%20both%20decided%20that%20they%20would%20live%20together.%20So%20when%20both%20of%20them%20came%20before%20the%20Lok%20Adalat%20court%2C%20I%20asked%20them%2C%20and%20they%20said%20that%20they%20had%20decided%20to%20live%20together%20happily.%20The%20wife%20said%20that%20I%20do%20not%20want%20maintenance%20because%20we%20are%20living%20together%20very%20happily.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20the%20idea%20of%20Lok%20Adalat%20is%20to%20settle%20small%20cases.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20do%20not%20realize%20how%20many%20small%20cases%20come%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20We%20choose%20cases%20like%20service%2C%20labour%20disputes%2C%20land%20acquisition%2C%20and%20motor%20accident%20claim%20cases%20to%20hear%20in%20the%20Lok%20Adalat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20presence%20of%20bar%20members%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Lok%20Adalat%20panel%20along%20with%20judges%20has%20given%20the%20right%20message%20to%20the%20entire%20society%20that%20we%20are%20united%20in%20our%20efforts%20to%20do%20justice%2C%20especially%20to%20the%20citizens%20involved%20in%20these%20small%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandra