ed%20that%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%20promising%20to%20be%20a%20game%20changer%2C%20but%20ended%20up%20becoming%20just%20a%20%26quot%3Bname%20changer%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20government%20did%20not%20provide%20enough%20funds%20in%20the%20budget%20for%20several%20schemes%20the%20saffron%20party%20promised%20in%20its%20election%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20participating%20in%20the%20general%20discussion%20on%20the%20annual%20budget%20for%20fiscal%202024-25%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20president%20asserted%20that%20the%20BJP%20altered%20the%20names%20of%2045%20schemes%20of%20the%20previous%20BJD%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Charan%20Majhi%2C%20who%20also%20holds%20the%20finance%20portfolio%2C%20presented%20the%20BJP%20government's%20maiden%20budget%20on%20July%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20said%20its%20government%20will%20be%20a%20game%20changer%2C%20but%20unfortunately%20it%20has%20ended%20up%20being%20a%20name%20changer.%20It%20has%20presented%20a%20name-changing%20and%20colour-changing%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Patnaik%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Odisha%20for%20five%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20previous%20BJD%20administration's%20schemes%20were%20repeated%20in%20the%20BJP%20government's%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20formed%20the%20government%20by%20promising%20people%20that%20they%20would%20bring%20paribartan%20(change).%20After%20going%20through%20the%20budget%20documents%2C%20I%20find%20this%20government%20has%20changed%20the%20names%20of%2045%20schemes%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20BJD%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20shows%20the%20robustness%2C%20pro-people%20and%20progressive%20character%20of%20the%20schemes%20designed%20and%20implemented%20by%20the%20BJD%20government%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Mr%20Patnaik%20did%20not%20explain%20what%20he%20meant%20by%20%26quot%3Bcolour%20change%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20apparently%20referred%20to%20the%20change%20of%20the%20colour%20of%20LAccMI%20buses%20(an%20affordable%20bus%20service%20for%20villagers)%20from%20green%20to%20saffron%20after%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMentioning%20several%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%20before%20the%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Patnaik%20claimed%20that%20the%20budget%20did%20not%20provision%20for%20funds%20required%20to%20implement%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20will%20need%20Rs%20one%20lakh%20crore%20to%20implement%20the%20Subhadra%20scheme%20but%20the%20budget%20mentioned%20only%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20cover%20less%20than%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20over%20two%20crore%20women%20of%20Odisha.%20What%20about%20the%20rest%201.80%20crore%20women%3F%20Mr%20Patnaik%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20scheme%20named%20after%20Lord%20Jagannath's%20sister%2C%20cash%20vouchers%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20will%20be%20provided%20to%20women%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patnaik%20said%20the%20BJP%20promised%20to%20increase%20social%20security%20pension%20to%20Rs%203%2C500%20per%20month.%20There%20are%20about%2050%20lakh%20pensioners%20in%20the%20state%2C%20out%20of%20which%20hardly%20one%20lakh%20will%20benefit%20as%20per%20the%20budget%20allocation%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20rest%2049%20lakh%20pensioners%20between%20the%20age%20of%20sixty%20years%20to%20eighty%20years%20of%20age%20including%20widows%2C%20PWDs%20and%20distressed%20people%3F%20You%20need%20about%20Rs%2021%2C000%20crore%20per%20year%20to%20fulfil%20this%20promise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20BJP's%20announcement%20of%20Rs%203100%20as%20MSP%20per%20quintal%20of%20paddy%20to%20farmers%2C%20Patnaik%20said%20that%20the%20allocation%20kept%20in%20the%20budget%20will%20not%20be%20adequate%20to%20cover%20even%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20peasants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20apart%2C%20Mr%20Patnaik%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20promised%203000%20units%20of%20free%20electricity.%20The%20Central%20government%20has%20planned%20free%20power%20for%20one%20crore%20houses%20for%20the%20entire%20country%20and%20Odisha's%20share%20may%20be%20three%20lakh%20houses%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20one%20and%20half%20crore%20houses%20in%20the%20state.%20Is%20this%20the%20free%20electricity%20you%20promised%20to%20the%20people%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patnaik%20claimed%20that%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20the%20BJP%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20cover%20even%20five%20per%20cent%20of%20Odisha's%20population%20under%20the%203000%20units%20of%20free%20electricity%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20create%2025%20lakh%20'Lakhpati%20Didis'%20(self-help%20group%20members)%20by%202027%20as%20promised%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20government%20will%20need%20about%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%2C%20while%20the%20allocation%20is%20only%20Rs%201%2C000%20core%20for%20this%2C%20Patnaik%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20demanded%20that%20the%20government%20table%20the%20detailed%20list%20of%20'Lakhpati%20Didis'%20in%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20BJP's%20promise%20of%20a%20developed%20Odisha%20by%202036%2C%20Mr%20Patnaik%20said%20the%20budget%20provides%20Rs%2020%20crore%20for%20the%20industrial%20corridor%20connecting%20Rourkela-Sambalpur-Paradip%20and%20Dhamra%20by%20June%202027.%20A%20corridor%20like%20this%20will%20not%20cost%20less%20than%20Rs%20one%20lakh%20crore%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharpening%20his%20criticism%20of%20the%20government%2C%20the%20BJD%20president%20described%20the%20BJP%20as%20a%20'Jumla'%20(gimmick)%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp