fford%20to%20eat%20vegetables%20anymore%20and%20survived%20on%20%3Cem%3Enamak%20roti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(salt%20and%20flatbread)%20for%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20Krishna%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Delhi%20to%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20place%20in%20search%20of%20work.%20With%20only%20Rs%20500%20in%20her%20pocket%2C%20she%20relocated%20to%20the%20city%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20their%20three%20young%20children.%20%E2%80%9CI%20looked%20for%20jobs%2C%20but%20without%20any%20formal%20education%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20work.%20My%20husband%20also%20struggled%20to%20find%20employment.%20After%20two%20months%2C%20we%20began%20working%20on%20a%20field%20through%20sharecropping%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharecropping%20is%20a%20legal%20arrangement%20where%20a%20landowner%20permits%20a%20tenant%20to%20cultivate%20their%20land%2C%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20crops%20produced.%20The%20five-member%20family%20began%20living%20in%20a%20small%20room%20on%20the%20field.%20They%20spent%20their%20days%20cultivating%20vegetables%2C%20but%20the%20income%20from%20their%20efforts%20was%20insufficient%20to%20sustain%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20price%20of%20vegetables%20in%20the%20market%20would%20fluctuate%20and%20we%20would%20hardly%20earn%20any%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2055-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Starting%20with%20karonda%20(black%20currants)%2C%20she%20introduced%20a%20variety%20of%20pickles%2C%20including%20mangoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20and%20lemons.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303.jpg