0currants)%20from%20her%20field%2C%20a%20few%20spices%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20utensils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20grew%20up%20seeing%20my%20%3Cem%3Edadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Enani%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandmothers)%20make%20pickles%2C%20the%20know-how%20that%20I%20learnt%20in%20the%20training%20was%20insightful.%20As%20homemakers%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20really%20calculate%20the%20amounts%20of%20spices%20and%20salt%20to%20be%20added%20to%20the%20pickle.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20taught%20ways%20to%20enhance%20the%20taste%20as%20well%20as%20the%20shelf%20life%20of%20pickles%20naturally.%20The%20key%20was%20the%20measurement%20of%20spices%20and%20oils%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20Krishna%20started%20making%20the%20pickles%2C%20but%20she%20had%20little%20knowledge%20of%20commercialising%20the%20products.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20set%20up%20a%20small%20table%20on%20the%20roadside%20and%20put%20our%20products%20on%20display.%20It%20was%20not%20a%20very%20busy%20road%20but%20we%20wanted%20to%20attract%20people%20to%20our%20stall.%20So%2C%20we%20placed%20two%20large%20earthen%20pots%20of%20water%20along%20with%20the%20pickles.%20I%20offered%20pickles%20as%20samples%20to%20those%20who%20stopped%20to%20drink%20free%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20simple%20yet%20effective%20strategy%20slowly%20built%20her%20customer%20base.%20She%20also%20started%20participating%20in%20local%20fairs%20to%20promote%20the%20products.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20her%20pickles%20grew%2C%20allowing%20her%20to%20formally%20launch%20her%20company%20%E2%80%98Shri%20Krishna%20Pickles%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20eventually%20open%20her%20own%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20%3Cem%3Ekaronda%20%3C%2Fem%3E(black%20currants)%2C%20she%20introduced%20a%20variety%20of%20pickles%2C%20including%20mangoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20and%20lemons.%20Today%2C%20she%20offers%20over%20250%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopene