0nostalgic%20taste.%20Their%20wide%20variety%20of%20flavours%20caters%20to%20every%20palate%20and%20mood.%20Whenever%20I%20open%20one%20of%20their%20jars%2C%20it%20bursts%20with%20authentic%20tastes%20and%20aromas%2C%20enhancing%20my%20simple%20meals.%20These%20pickles%20never%20disappoint%2C%20consistently%20maintaining%20their%20taste%20and%20quality%20over%20the%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%20has%20established%20a%20five-storey%20facility%20in%20Delhi%2C%20where%20she%20manufactures%2010%20to%2020%20quintals%20of%20pickles%20daily%2C%20and%20her%20company%20boasts%20an%20impressive%20annual%20turnover%20of%20Rs%205%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20her%20extraordinary%20determination%20and%20entrepreneurial%20spirit%2C%20she%20has%20been%20recognised%20with%20multiple%20awards%20including%20the%20Outstanding%20Women%20Award%20from%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20International%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Day%202012%3B%20the%20Innovative%20Award%20for%20Agriculture%20and%20allied%20activities%20during%20the%20Global%20Agriculture%20Summit%202013%3B%20and%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Award%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20her%20journey%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20homemaker%20and%20my%20core%20job%20was%20to%20look%20after%20the%20household%20duties.%20But%20I%20wanted%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20family%20income%20in%20our%20dire%20times.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20let%20my%20children%20face%20the%20brunt%20of%20our%20financial%20crisis.%20It%20was%20a%20small%20step%2C%20and%20I%20never%20imagined%20I%20would%20come%20this%20far.%E2%80%9D%20She%20adds%20that%20her%20husband%20and%20eldest%20son%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20business%2C%20while%20her%20other%20two%20children%20are%20currently%20pursuing%20their%20higher%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20have%20both%20%3Cem%3Egaadi%20bangla%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20car%20and%20a%20bungalow)%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20dignity%20to%20walk%20with%20pride.%20As%20a%20child%2C%20I%20aspired%20to%20be%20on%20television%2C%20and%20that%20dream%20came%20true%20with%20my%20business.%20However%2C%20achieving%20this%20success%20required%20consistent%20hard%20work.%20If%20I%20were%20to%20stop%20now%2C%20I%20would%20risk%20losing%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20example%2C%20Krishna%20emphasises%20the%20transformative%20power%20of%20adversity%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20resilience.%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20be%20bogged%20down%20by%20failures.%20Do%20not%20view%20helplessness%20or%20failure%20as%20a%20setback%20but%20as%20a%20stepping%20stone%20to%20greater%20achievements.%20If%20one%20door%20closes%2C%20many%20others%20open%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Shri%20Krishna%20Pickles.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722240366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358846%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Krishna%20Yadav%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20from%20a%20small%20village%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20She%20began%20selling%20pickles%20on%20the%20roadside.%20Eventually%2C%20she%20established%20%E2%80%98Shri%20Krishna%20Pickles%E2%80%99%2C%20growing%20her%20business%20into%20a%20successful%20enterprise%20with%20over%20250%20varieties%20of%20products%20and%20a%20five-storey%20factory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358846%2Futtar-pradesh-krishna-yadav-pickle-business-delhi-earn-crores-woman-empowerment%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Microsoft%20outage%3A%20Cyber%20security%20agency%20has%20%E2%80%98warning%20on%20CrowdStrike%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22