%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A74%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Finternational-olympic-committee-says-gender-parity-in-football-too-expensive-13186397%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Finternational-olympic-committee-says-gender-parity-in-football-too-expensive-13186397%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Finternational-olympic-committee-says-gender-parity-in-football-too-expensive-13186397%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CSR%20Initiative%20Helps%20Youth%20in%20Rural%20India%20with%20Skills%20Training%2C%20Has%20Empowered%203%20Lakh%20Workers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESubhajit%20Das%20dropped%20out%20of%20school%20after%20Class%206%20due%20to%20personal%20circumstances.%20He%20was%20often%20mocked%20and%20questioned%20about%20what%20he%20could%20achieve%20without%20completing%20his%20education.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20determined%20to%20prove%20them%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20millions%20of%20rural%20school%20dropouts%20in%20the%20country%20like%20Subhajit%2C%20who%20have%20the%20grit%20and%20determination%20to%20achieve%20goals%20but%20are%20unable%20to%20grow%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20skill%20training.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.larsentoubro.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELarsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20(L%26amp%3BT)%3C%2Fa%3E%20decided%20to%20bridge%20this%20gap%20in%20the%20construction%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstruction%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20second-largest%20employer%20after%20the%20agriculture%20sector.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EKnight%20Frank%20%26amp%3B%20RICS%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%2071%20million%20workers%20are%20estimated%20to%20be%20employed%20in%20this%20sector%2C%20but%20only%2019%20percent%20are%20skilled%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20industry%20is%20poised%20for%20significant%20growth%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20underscoring%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20skilled%20labour.%20To%20meet%20this%20demand%2C%20vocational%20training%20in%20construction%20has%20become%20essential%2C%20equipping%20the%20workforce%20with%20specialised%20skills%20vital%20for%20the%20sector%E2%80%99s%20advancement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnticipating%20this%20need%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20launched%20the%20first%20Construction%20Skills%20Training%20Institute%20(CSTI)%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20in%201995.%20This%20initiative%20aimed%20to%20develop%20a%20cadre%20of%20well-trained%20professionals%20for%20the%20construction%20industry.%20Over%20the%20past%20three%20decades%2C%20CSTI%20has%20expanded%20to%20nine%20operational%20institutes%2C%20training%20over%203.4%20lakh%20workers%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkilled%20youth%20trained%20at%20these%20CSTIs%20are%20now%20employed%20by%20top%20construction%20companies%20across%20the%20country%2C%20including%20L%26amp%3BT%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20skilled%20workers%20to%20boost%20livelihoods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20goals%20behind%20this%20endeavour%20by%20the%20company%20is%20to%20help%20underprivileged%20rural%20youth%20become%20self-reliant%20through%20this%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-1722002541.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22L%26amp%3BT%20runs%20nine%20CSTIs%20in%20the%20country%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-1722002541.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-1722002541-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-1722002541-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-1722002541-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-1722002541-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EL%26amp%3BT%20runs%20nine%20CSTIs%20in%20the%20country%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStudies%20indicated%20that%20a%20substantial%20portion%20of%20the%20workforce%20in%20the%20construction%20sector%20was%20unskilled%20or%20semi-skilled.%20Recognising%20the%20need%20for%20a%20skilled%20workforce%20to%20undertake%20basic%20infrastructure%20work%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20established%20the%20CSTI.%20The%20primary%20goal%20is%20to%20equip%20underprivileged%20youth%20with%20various%20construction-based%20skills%2C%20thereby%20enhancing%20their%20employability%20and%20contributing%20to%20the%20industry%E2%80%99s%20workforce%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mabel%20Abraham%2C%20Head%2C%20Corporate%20Social%20Initiatives%20at%20Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20initiatives%20by%20L%26amp%3BT%20also%20came%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20construction%20industry%20saw%20an%20influx%20of%20new%20technologies%20that%20increased%20the%20demand%20for%20skilled%20manpower.%20One%20of%20the%20objectives%20of%20this%20vocational%20training%20was%20to%20address%20this%20growing%20industry%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CSTIs%20have%20a%20meticulously%20designed%20curriculum%20that%20caters%20to%20both%20newcomers%20and%20the%20less%20experienced%20segments%20of%20the%20workforce%2C%20progressively%20enhancing%20their%20expertise%20across%20various%20construction%20trades.%20The%20courses%20are%20tailored%20to%20underprivileged%20individuals%20from%20marginalised%20backgrounds%2C%20aged%2018%20to%2035%2C%20who%20have%20passed%20Class%205.%20Trainees%20are%20selected%20through%20a%20process%20that%20includes%20an%20entrance%20test%20(both%20written%20and%20practical)%20and%20a%20viva%20voce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CSTIs%20offer%20a%20variety%20of%20courses%20tailored%20to%20the%20construction%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20including%20formwork%20carpentry%2C%20bar%20bending%2C%20steel%20fixing%2C%20masonry%20(brickwork%20and%20block%20work)%2C%20plumbing%2C%20sanitary%2C%20electrical%20work%2C%20scaffolding%2C%20welding%2C%20tiling%2C%20and%20pipe%20welding.%20They%20also%20include%20courses%20related%20to%20smart%20city%20projects%2C%20such%20as%20optical%20fibre%20cable%20(OFC)%20and%20CCTV%20Installation%2C%20solar%20panel%20installation%2C%20and%20metro%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-2-1722003002.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20CSTIs%20offer%20a%20variety%20of%20courses%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-2-1722003002.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-2-1722003002-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-2-1722003002-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-2-1722003002-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-2-1722003002-1536x1024.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-2-1722003002-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358794%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20CSTIs%20offer%20a%20variety%20of%20courses%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20courses%20are%20short-term%2C%20typically%20lasting%20200%20hours%20over%20a%20month%20or%20600%20hours%20over%20three%20months.%20The%20training%20is%2080%20percent%20practical%20and%2020%20percent%20classroom-based.%20Trainees%20receive%20free%20lodging%20and%20food%20at%20the%20centres.%20L%26amp%3BT%E2%80%99s%20construction%20sites%20serve%20as%20a%20learning%20ground%20for%20trainees%20during%20their%20internships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENiharika%20Malik%2C%20trainer%20at%20CSTI%2C%20Mayurbhanj%20for%20Advance%20Masonry%20says%20that%20they%20train%20students%20to%20handle%20life%E2%80%99s%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20give%20them%20technical%20knowledge%20about%20bricks%2C%20identifying%20good%20quality%20cement%2C%20how%20to%20ensure%20safety%20while%20working%20and%20more.%20Besides%20this%2C%20we%20also%20focus%20on%20building%20their%20personality%20and%20soft%20skills%2C%20and%20making%20them%20technically%20strong.%20We%20equip%20them%20to%20handle%20any%20challenge%20that%20life%20may%20throw%20at%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98My%20fortunes%20have%20turned%20around%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20skill%20training%20hub%20was%20inaugurated%20in%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Mayurbhanj%20district%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20in%20her%20hometown%20in%20November%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpread%20over%20five%20acres%2C%20this%20skill%20training%20hub%20is%20equipped%20to%20accommodate%20120%20trainees%2C%20has%20practice%20yards%20for%20various%20trades%2C%20and%20a%20dedicated%20workshop%20for%20learning%20pipe%20welding.%20It%20is%20equipped%20with%20the%20latest%20technology%20to%20enhance%20the%20quality%20of%20learning%2C%20including%20simulators%20with%20AR%2FVR%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20