india.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKandal-1721985731-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKandal-1721985731-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKandal-1721985731-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKandal-1721985731-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358685%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKandal%20Rajan%20has%20planted%20mangroves%20along%20the%20Pazhayangadi%20River%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20the%20Kannur%20district%20of%20Kerala%2C%20Kandal%20Rajan%20(%3Cem%3Ekandal%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20nickname%20which%20translates%20to%20mangrove)%20has%20been%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20restore%20the%20mangrove%20cover%20along%20the%20Pazhayangadi%20River.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20over%20four%20decades%20but%20Rajan%E2%80%99s%20spark%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20dimmed%20one%20bit.%20He%20comes%20from%20a%20long%20line%20of%20fisherfolk%20and%20says%20this%20has%20given%20him%20an%20insight%20into%20how%20ecosystems%20are%20critical%20to%20the%20fishing%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20witnessed%20their%20degradation%20over%20the%20past%20several%20years.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F277743%2Ffisherman-canoe-mangrove-conservation-nursery-kerala-kandal-rajan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThese%20mangroves%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20also%20the%20breeding%20ground%20for%20fish%20and%20several%20other%20marine%20and%20non-marine%20species.%20I%20have%20seen%20around%2022%20species%20of%20mangroves%20in%20these%20regions%2C%20but%20now%20most%20of%20them%20have%20disappeared%20mainly%20due%20to%20human%20intervention.%20They%20are%20being%20extensively%20cut%20down%20for%20shrimp%20or%20paddy%20cultivation.%20So%2C%20the%20least%20I%20can%20do%20is%20to%20plant%20more%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20he%20has%20planted%201%2C50%2C000%20mangroves%20while%20his%20home%20nursery%20boasts%2025%2C000%20saplings%20of%20various%20varieties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20step%20towards%20augmenting%20India%E2%80%99s%20mangrove%20cover%2C%20the%20Union%20budget%202023-24%20announced%20the%20%E2%80%98Mangrove%20Initiative%20for%20Shoreline%20Habitats%20%26amp%3B%20Tangible%20Incomes%20(MISHTI)%E2%80%99%20programme.%20The%20project%20is%20aimed%20at%20protecting%20and%20reviving%20mangrove%20ecosystems%20on%20the%20Indian%20coast%20while%20enhancing%20the%20socio-economic%20status%20of%20coastal%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unep.org%2Fnews-and-stories%2Fstory%2Finside-look-beauty-and-benefits-mangroves%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAn%20inside%20look%20at%20the%20beauty%20and%20benefits%20of%20mangroves%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20UNEP%2C%20Published%20on%2025%20July%202023.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1947426%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStatus%20of%20Mangrove%20Plantations%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%2C%20Published%20on%2010%20August%202023.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffsi.nic.in%2Fisfr-2021%2Fchapter-3.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMangrove%20Cover